snippet.title: Diana and Roma playing Professions
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma playing Professions. Roma tries himself in the profession of astronaut and fireman. Diana - as an ice cream seller. Children come to the conclusion that these professions do not suit them. Dad suggests Diana and Roma just to be children - play & jump on a trampoline.
